{"tid":801294,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打用uber養車？","createTime":"2018-08-31T13:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T01:31:13.000Z","uid":2621,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b8d9fdf38bb5383c14d7fb07e2b7cf6695198bce","tid":801294,"uid":2621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:40:11.000Z","msg":"自己有部錢七，自己一個夠用<br />\n但係黎緊要成日車女朋友同佢屋企人<br />\n想換架好少少既車但係又想keep住儲錢<br />\n諗住出部十幾萬既慳油車上會供<br />\n有時間用返uber跑返條供車數有冇得諗<br />\n或者有冇巴打有類似經驗分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a4ccf060f779393eb2c8e53f0af3a3418fc93c","tid":801294,"uid":2621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515213281feede193225aa379169a3980a5c41c8","tid":801294,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:13:17.000Z","msg":"邊有得做 賺得黎都蝕曬<br />\n利申：同你有過一樣諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4ebdbd774c9873bab496cbe943cdcc86bcf4a1","tid":801294,"uid":55125,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:16:36.000Z","msg":"本末倒置啊巴打 <br />\n我情願渣的士的唔會渣uber <br />\n一黎 可以出自己鍾意車 <br />\n二黎uber 無咁多單"},{"pid":"f81725a9e8274cfc0409ce22564d0c51979664c7","tid":801294,"uid":57424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:18:18.000Z","msg":"上年尾冇野做，玩左三日冇再做<br />\n搞錢小又要入油"},{"pid":"5fd14257d6cd00b15d0a3851a35158b72383fc99","tid":801294,"uid":2621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ec4ebdbd774c9873bab496cbe943cdcc86bcf4a1","tid":801294,"uid":55125,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:16:36.000Z","msg":"本末倒置啊巴打 <br />\n我情願渣的士的唔會渣uber <br />\n一黎 可以出自己鍾意車 <br />\n二黎uber 無咁多單"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T16:35:57.000Z","msg":"我想彈性時間跑，又搵唔到同等part time"},{"pid":"73b4f7c43f2531ed8a2691aabfc93f9ea9e7f8b9","tid":801294,"uid":158074,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T16:39:43.000Z","msg":"做uber, 隨時比人捉。而且賺埋D錢，第時賣車咁高里數，要平賣。計起上黎真係有數圍？"},{"pid":"e615cf3f7fc410b4adf12c34f650b424b45f2fc3","tid":801294,"uid":2621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9efd4d9dfb25e9a9747e176e7056a47d06d25a6","tid":801294,"uid":39049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:34:52.000Z","msg":"唔建議用新車做uber"},{"pid":"ffaae246b58bf3c90358fc7233726c02028479ee","tid":801294,"uid":39049,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:38:44.000Z","msg":"你買部十年車齡內四門車, 建議混能, 純電或者柴油, 唔建議電油車, 因為扣埋油錢冇乜肉食, 亦唔建議買新車做, 因為你都唔想新車落地就咁快俾陌生人坐殘.<br />\n<br />\n之後你安裝司機apps, 申請account, upload 頭像, 身份證, 車牌, 牌簿, 保險, 一般嚟講兩三日就批到, 咁你就可以開始開機接客.<br />\n<br />\n不過有以下風險, 自己衡量承受能力至決定做唔做<br />\n<br />\n1. 目前運作模式係走緊灰色地帶, 因為你部車係冇出租汽車許可證, 會衰非法載客取酬, 隨時有機會遇到差佬放蛇, 拉人兼封艇.<br />\n<br />\n2. 亦正因為非法載客取酬, 而一般汽車三保會講明唔包商業或取酬用途, 萬一載客途中發生意外, 俾保險公司查到你當時做緊uber, 你份三保會凍過水, uber 果份三保只會保乘客, 唔會保司機, 換言之, 你炒爛咗人哋部車, 對家claim 唔到你份三保, 到時你分分鐘破產都唔掂.<br />\n<br />\n都係果句, 做就唔好驚, 驚就唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32e4ad6f5aba56f5a01e4c16c0e5f678d8834b1","tid":801294,"uid":39049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73b4f7c43f2531ed8a2691aabfc93f9ea9e7f8b9","tid":801294,"uid":158074,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T16:39:43.000Z","msg":"做uber, 隨時比人捉。而且賺埋D錢，第時賣車咁高里數，要平賣。計起上黎真係有數圍？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:39:57.000Z","msg":"所以買二手車做好過出新車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93090cdd47857b096f04fc1d8d94bca25a418d93","tid":801294,"uid":2621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffaae246b58bf3c90358fc7233726c02028